# Initial Backlog Ideas – MyClean App

## User Stories

| # | User Story | Priority | Estimate (Days) |
|--|------------|----------|-----------------|
| 1 | As a cleaner, I want to create and manage my profile, so customers can find me. | High | 3 |
| 2 | As a customer, I want to book a cleaner through a calendar, so I can choose times. | High | 5 |
| 3 | As a cleaner, I want real-time booking alerts, so I don’t miss jobs. | Medium | 2 |
| 4 | As a customer, I want to pay online securely, so I don’t need cash. | High | 4 |
| 5 | As a cleaner, I want to view earnings and stats, to track my work. | Medium | 3 |
| 6 | As a customer, I want to leave reviews, so others can benefit. | Medium | 2 |
| 7 | As a cleaner, I want to manage my availability calendar. | High | 3 |
| 8 | As a customer, I want to message the cleaner in-app. | Low | 2 |
| 9 | As an admin, I want to verify cleaner profiles. | Low | 4 |
| 10 | As a customer, I want to choose eco-friendly services. | Low | 2 |

---
